snippet.title: Custom Party - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam : store.steampowered.com/app/2904730/Custom_Party/

*Demo coming on October 14th 2024.*

*GAME DESCRIPTION*
Custom Party is a free indie party-game.
Players can use different powers (dash, explosion...) and have different stats based on their character customization.
It introduces an innovative ranking system named «Take a Risk».
The game allows everybody to play in the playstyle they want.
